Reasoning: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a new method of integrating Fourier methods into recurrent neural networks for data processing, which falls under the umbrella of machine learning. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper specifically focuses on complex recurrent neural network architectures, which falls under the category of neural computing. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new method for improving accuracy and reducing computational load in data analysis and prediction tasks, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper demonstrates the effectiveness of the proposed method on real-world human motion prediction, which falls under the category of computer vision. 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper also demonstrates the effectiveness of the proposed method on music recognition, which falls under the category of sound.
